    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors were fully assessed and met or exceeded required levels for Model Risk Level 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was carried as not-assessed on the basis that the validation and COU geometries and operating conditions are identical, which the team judged to render a formal equivalency argument redundant. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
